@startuml seq-item-detail-operations
title ItemDetailPage ボタン操作シーケンス

actor "ユーザー" as User
participant "ItemDetailPage" as Page
participant "useDisclosure\n(composable)" as Disclosure
participant "ConfirmSheet" as Confirm
participant "useGetItem\n(Vue Query)" as Query
participant "useUpdateItem\n(Mutation)" as UpdateM
participant "useDeleteItem\n(Mutation)" as DeleteM
participant "useInvalidateItems\n(composable)" as Invalidate
participant "customFetch\n(mutator.ts)" as Fetch
participant "MSW Handler\n(handlers.ts)" as Handler
participant "store.ts" as Store
participant "Vue Router" as Router

== ページ初期表示（データ取得）==

Router -> Page : /items/:id へナビゲート
Page -> Query : useGetItem(id)\n→ GET /api/items/:id
Query -> Fetch : fetch('/api/items/:id')
Fetch -> Handler : http.get('*/api/items/:id')
Handler -> Store : store.get(id)

alt アイテムが存在する
  Store --> Handler : Item
  Handler --> Fetch : HttpResponse.json(item, 200)
  Fetch --> Query : data: Item
  Query -> Page : watch(data):\n  form に初期値セット
  Page -> User : フォームにデータを表示
else アイテムが存在しない（404）
  Store --> Handler : undefined
  Handler --> Fetch : HttpResponse(null, 404)
  Fetch --> Query : isError: true
  Page -> User : 「項目が見つかりません（404）」表示
end

== 保存ボタン押下 ==

User -> Page : フォーム編集後「保存」をタップ
Page -> UpdateM : save():\n  updateMutation.mutate({ id, data: form })
UpdateM -> Fetch : PUT /api/items/:id\nBody: ItemInput JSON
Fetch -> Handler : http.put('*/api/items/:id')
Handler -> Store : store.update(id, body)
Store --> Handler : 更新後の Item
Handler --> Fetch : HttpResponse.json(item, 200)
Fetch --> UpdateM : 更新成功

UpdateM -> Invalidate : onSuccess:\n  invalidateItems()
Invalidate -> Invalidate : queryClient.invalidateQueries(...)
UpdateM -> Router : router.back()
Router -> User : 前画面（ItemListPage）へ戻る

== 削除ボタン押下 → 確認シート ==

User -> Page : 「削除」をタップ
Page -> Disclosure : openConfirm()
Disclosure -> Disclosure : isOpen = true
Disclosure --> Page : showConfirm = true
Page -> Confirm : [props] isOpen = true\ntitle / destructive
Confirm -> User : 確認 ActionSheet 表示

alt ユーザーが「削除」を選択
  User -> Confirm : 「削除」ボタンをタップ
  Confirm -> Page : [emit] confirmed
  Page -> DeleteM : remove():\n  deleteMutation.mutate({ id })
  DeleteM -> Fetch : DELETE /api/items/:id
  Fetch -> Handler : http.delete('*/api/items/:id')
  Handler -> Store : store.remove(id)
  Handler --> Fetch : HttpResponse(null, 204)
  Fetch --> DeleteM : 削除成功

  DeleteM -> Invalidate : onSuccess:\n  invalidateItems()
  Invalidate -> Invalidate : queryClient.invalidateQueries(...)
  DeleteM -> Router : router.replace('/items')
  Router -> User : ItemListPage へ遷移

else ユーザーがキャンセル
  User -> Confirm : 「キャンセル」or バックドロップ
  Confirm -> Page : [emit] cancelled
  Page -> Disclosure : closeConfirm()
  Disclosure -> Disclosure : isOpen = false
  Disclosure --> Page : showConfirm = false
  Page -> Confirm : [props] isOpen = false
  Confirm -> User : ActionSheet を閉じる
end

@enduml
